- if policy(@project).update?
  #project_warning.bootstrap-alert
    .alert.alert-warning
      i Bem-vindo ao Rascunho!
      #toggle_warning
        = link_to '(minimizar informações)', '#'
      #project_warning_text
        br/
        br/
        | To edit the page of your project look below the <strong>ISSUE tab</strong>, perform all the changes to the form and click <strong>UPDATE INFORMATION</strong>.
